title: Crunch Report: Prince returns to Spotify
text:
By Anthony Ha Today’s Stories 
Prince returns to Spotify and Napster this weekend WhatsApp now supports two-step authentication Amazon’s Tap speaker gets a hands-free update in defiance of its name Beats X bring Apple’s wireless headphone tech to a tethered form factor 
Credits Written and hosted by: Anthony Ha Edited by: Joe Zolnoski
